{"document_id":"dbc58833497017c1c8c77f9e5e532906","filename":"Auria_Project_Info.md","relative_path":"Auria_Project_Info.md","section":"04_17_auria","has_text":true,"chunk_count":7,"full_text":"\\\"X_centroid\\\", \\\"Y_centroid\\\", \\\"imageid\\\", \\\"core_imageid\\\",\n\\\"cores.x\\\", \\\"celltype\\\", \\\"Annotation\\\", \\\"Stage\\\",\n\\\"patient_id_AB19_1654\\\", \\\"Area\\\", \\\"Eccentricity\\\",\n\\\"antioxidant_NQOI\\\", \\\"antioxidant_GCLC\\\", \\\"antioxidant_TXNRD1\\\",\n\\\"antioxidant_GLUT1\\\"\n\n\\\"spatial_kmeans\\\",\\\"marker_Ki67\\\",\\\"marker_PCNA\\\",\\\"classified_NQO1_Vim\\\",\\\"classified_GLUT1_Vim\\\"\n\n# Datasets\n\n## **13 TMAs**\n\n***All images***\n\n\\[\\'19_02_02A\\', \\'M1\\', \\'19_02_01A\\', \\'T2\\', \\'INF2\\', \\'19_02_03A\\',\n\\'1B\\', \\'2B\\', \\'3B\\', \\'INF1\\', \\'INF3\\', \\'T3\\', \\'T1\\'\\]\n\n\\*remove TMAs images, because some functional markers are not work\n\n\\[\\'19_02_02A\\', \\'19_02_01A\\', \\'T2\\', \\'INF2\\', \\'19_02_03A\\', \\'1B\\',\n\\'2B\\', \\'3B\\', \\'INF1\\'\\]\n\n+-----------------------------------+-----------------------------------+\n| ## **Cell_counts** | ![](media/image5. |\n| | png){width=\"0.8020833333333334in\" |\n| | height=\"1.9479166666666667in\"} |\n+===================================+===================================+\n+-----------------------------------+-----------------------------------+\n\n## **General info**\n\n***Dataset with all images***\n\n- 4,150,343 cells\n\n- 13 TMA images\n\n- 368 TMA cores\n\n - Core location\n\n - Tumor center (n = 194)\n\n - Invasive border (n = 70)\n\n - Inflammation (n = 70)\n\n - Lymph node met (n = 34)\n\n- 191 TNBC patients\n\n - Tumor stage\n\n - 1 (n = 49)\n\n - 2 (n = 94)\n\n - 3 (n = 11)\n\n - 4 (n = 2)\n\n- Invasive border (n = 70)\n\n - Inflammation (n = 70)\n\n - Lymph node met (n = 34)\n\n- 191 TNBC patients\n\n - Tumor stage\n\n - 1 (n = 49)\n\n - 2 (n = 94)\n\n - 3 (n = 11)\n\n - 4 (n = 2)\n\n - Unknown (n = 35)\n\n - Survival time and status\n\n***Dataset after removing some images***\n\n- 3,681,772 cells\n\n- 9 TMA images\n\n- 345 TMA cores\n\n - Core location\n\n - Tumor center (n = 192)\n\n - Invasive border (n = 66)\n\n - Inflammation (n = 61)\n\n - Lymph node met (n = 26)\n\n- 186 patients\n\n - Tumor stage\n\n - 1 (n = 49)\n\n - 2 (n = 91)\n\n - 3 (n = 11)\n\n - 4 (n = 2)\n\n - Unknown (n = 33)\n\n - Survival time and status\n\n## **Marker list**\n\n### **All markers**\n\n***34 markers:***\n\n\\[\\\"H3.1\\\",\\\"pRPA32\\\",\\\"S9.6\\\",\\\"Ki67_1\\\",\\\"TNFR1\\\",\\\"HER3\\\",\\\"panCK\\\",\\\"SMA\\\",\\\"CD45\\\",\\\"Ki67_2\\\",\\\"CD4\\\",\\\"FOXP3\\\",\\\"CD8a\\\",\\\"CD11b\\\",\\\"CD68\\\",\\\"CD206\\\",\\\"PCNA\\\",\\\"ER\\\",\\\"HER2\\\",\\\"EGFR\\\",\\\"PR\\\",\\\"H2ax\\\",\\\"Vimentin\\\",\\\"H3K27me3\\\",\\\"E.Cadherin\\\",\\\"GCLC\\\",\\\"TXNRD1\\\",\\\"NQO1\\\",\\\"pERK\\\",\\\"TXN\\\",\\\"pSTAT3\\\",\\\"pS6_235\\\",\\\"pRB\\\",\\\"GLUT1\\\"\\]\n\n***Select some: 25 markers***\n\n\\[\\'S9.6\\', \\'HER3\\', \\'panCK\\', \\'SMA\\', \\'CD45\\', \\'Ki67_2\\', \\'CD4\\',\n\\'FOXP3\\', \\'CD8a\\', \\'CD11b\\', \\'CD68\\', \\'CD206\\', \\'H2ax\\',\n\\'Vimentin\\', \\'H3K27me3\\', \\'E.Cadherin\\', \\'GCLC\\', \\'TXNRD1\\',\n\\'NQO1\\', \\'pERK\\', \\'TXN\\', \\'pSTAT3\\', \\'pS6_235\\', \\'pRB\\',\n\\'GLUT1\\'\\]\n\n\\*Antiox markers\n\n### **Marker used in spatial expression**\n\n3\\', \\'E.Cadherin\\', \\'GCLC\\', \\'TXNRD1\\',\n\\'NQO1\\', \\'pERK\\', \\'TXN\\', \\'pSTAT3\\', \\'pS6_235\\', \\'pRB\\',\n\\'GLUT1\\'\\]\n\n\\*Antiox markers\n\n### **Marker used in spatial expression**\n\n\\[\\'S9.6\\', \\'HER3\\', \\'panCK\\', \\'SMA\\', \\'CD45\\', \\'Ki67_2\\', \\'CD4\\',\n\\'FOXP3\\', \\'CD8a\\', \\'CD11b\\', \\'CD68\\', \\'CD206\\', \\'H2ax\\',\n\\'Vimentin\\', \\'H3K27me3\\', \\'E.Cadherin\\', \\'GCLC\\', \\'TXNRD1\\',\n\\'NQO1\\', \\'pERK\\', \\'TXN\\', \\'pSTAT3\\', \\'pS6_235\\', \\'pRB\\',\n\\'GLUT1\\'\\]\n\n***Remove:***\n\n\\[\\'S9.6\\', \\'HER3\\', \\'panCK\\',